! --- Fin root (= wing tip) ---
! Xle[m]      Yle[m]      Zle[m]      Chord[m]    AInc[deg]
SECTION
  0.557291     0.943476     0.000000     0.176265     0.000000
NACA
0010

! --- Rudder inboard edge (eta = 0.15) ---
